{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Hintergrundbilder skalieren","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Backgrounds_and_Borders/Resizing_background_images","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">Die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/background-size\"><code>background-size</code></a> CSS Eigenschaft ermöglicht es, die Größe von Hintergrundbildern einzustellen, anstatt das voreingestellte Verhalten, das Bild auf die volle Größe zu kacheln, zu verwenden.</span>Man kann das Bild nach Wunsch nach oben oder unten skalieren.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tiling_a_large_image","title":"Kacheln eines großen Bildes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Nehmen wir ein großes Bild, ein 2982x2808 Firefox Logo. Wir wollen (auch wenn das höchstwahrscheinlichst ein grauenhaft schlechtes Seitendesign ergibt) vier Kopien dieses Bildes in ein 300x300 Pixel Quadrat kacheln, damit es so aussieht:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/8965/ss1.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>Das wird erreicht, indem wir folgendes CSS verwenden:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css;  highlight:[8] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.square</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>firefox_logo.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> solid 2px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white 0px 0px 2px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 16px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Man braucht für&nbsp; <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/background-size\"><code>background-size</code></a> kein Präfix mehr zu setzen, jedoch können&nbsp; Präfix-Versionen hinzugefügt werden, wenn ältere Browser angesprochen werden sollen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"stretching_an_image","title":"Dehnen eines Bildes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Sowohl die horizontale als auch die vertikale Größe des Bildes kann angegeben werden, wie hier angegeben:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px 150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>So sieht das Ergebnis aus:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/8967/ss2.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"scaling_an_image_up","title":"Hochskalieren eines Bildes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Auf der anderen Seite des Spektrums kann ein Bild im Hintergrund auch hochskaliert werden. Hier wird ein 32x32 Pixel favicon auf 300x300 Pixel skaliert:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/8969/ss3.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css; highlight:[5] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.square2</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>favicon.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> solid 2px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white 0px 0px 2px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 16px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Wie man sehen kann, ist das CSS im Grunde identisch, außer dem Namen der Bilddatei.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"special_values.3a_.22contain.22_and_.22cover.22","title":"Spezielle Werte: \"contain\" und \"cover\"","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Neben den <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> Werten, bietet die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/background-size\"><code>background-size</code></a> CSS Eigenschaft zwei spezielle Werte für Größen, <code>contain</code> und <code>cover</code>. Sehen wir uns diese an.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contain","title":"<code>contain</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Der contain Wert spezifiziert, unabhängig von der Größe der umgebenden Box, die Skalierung des Hintergrundbildes so, dass jede Seite so breit als irgend möglich angezeigt wird ohne über die Länge der korrespondierenden Seite des Containers hinauszugehen. Versuche mit einem Browser, der skalierende Hintergründe unterstützt (wie z. B.&nbsp; Firefox 3.6 oder höher), dieses Fenster in der Größe zu verändern, um das Verhalten am untenstehenden Live-Beispiel zu sehen.</p>\n\n<figure>\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"contain sample\" id=\"frame_contain\" width=\"100%\" height=\"220\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Backgrounds_and_Borders/Resizing_background_images/_sample_.contain.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n</figure>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bgSizeContain<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Try resizing this window and see what happens.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css;highlight:[4] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.bgSizeContain</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/8971/firefox_logo.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> contain<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid darkgray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px 1px 0 #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"contain"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cover","title":"<code>cover</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Der cover Wert spezifizert, dass das Hintergundbild in der Größe so angezeigt wird, dass es selbst so klein als möglich ist, dabei aber auf alle Fälle in beiden Dimensionen größer oder gleich der jeweiligen korresponierenden Maße des Containers ist.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<figure><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"cover sample\" id=\"frame_cover\" width=\"100%\" height=\"220\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Backgrounds_and_Borders/Resizing_background_images/_sample_.cover.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></figure>\n\n<p>Das Beispiel verwendet folgendes HTML &amp; CSS:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bgSizeCover<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Try resizing this window and see what happens.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css;highlight:[4] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.bgSizeCover</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/8971/firefox_logo.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> cover<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid darkgray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px 1px 0 #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"cover"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/background-size\"><code>background-size</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/background\"><code>background</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Kacheln eines großen Bildes","id":"tiling_a_large_image"},{"text":"Dehnen eines Bildes","id":"stretching_an_image"},{"text":"Hochskalieren eines Bildes","id":"scaling_an_image_up"},{"text":"Spezielle Werte: \"contain\" und \"cover\"","id":"special_values.3a_.22contain.22_and_.22cover.22"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Die background-size CSS Eigenschaft ermöglicht es, die Größe von Hintergrundbildern einzustellen, anstatt das voreingestellte Verhalten, das Bild auf die volle Größe zu kacheln, zu verwenden.","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Resizing background images with background-size","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Mettre à l'échelle des images en arrière-plan","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"背景画像の拡大縮小","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"배경 이미지 크기 조정하기","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Alterando a escala das imagens de background","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Scaling background images","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/css/css_backgrounds_and_borders/resizing_background_images","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/css/css_backgrounds_and_borders/resizing_background_images/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Backgrounds_and_Borders","title":"CSS Background and Borders"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Backgrounds_and_Borders/Resizing_background_images","title":"Hintergrundbilder skalieren"}],"pageTitle":"Hintergrundbilder skalieren - CSS | MDN","noIndexing":false}}